{"tid":1930012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"因為武漢肺炎同屋企人反面......","createTime":"2020-03-17T09:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T09:49:56.000Z","uid":268371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e7492ae5ce37c3a0b87b89c7c202ba38a5106fb","tid":1930012,"uid":268371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:36:29.000Z","msg":"抗爭以嚟因為政見唔同，受足藍絲老母經濟制裁。<br />\n<br />\n尋日難得返屋企想心平氣和食餐飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢聽我講武漢肺炎，<br />\n然後好認真咁話人地個正名叫「冠狀病毒」，<br />\n唔準我再話係武漢肺炎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我個人咁臭串當然繼續反駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢老跟住就話我仇視中国人，又話咩明明我流住中国嘅血，點解見到美國帶病毒入中国都唔幫返自己民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又叫我唔好再問佢攞生活費，咁唔鍾意做中国人就去問美國佬攞錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後完全反左面唔再返去，又冇工開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都幾迷惘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e98c1b14c379a5030785abf71f1541625c4c89","tid":1930012,"uid":273157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:37:24.000Z","msg":"你大概幾歲吖Ching"},{"pid":"4a17617dafde9920952632d7abdf2080e5131dc3","tid":1930012,"uid":18639,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:37:51.000Z","msg":"返住炒散先"},{"pid":"9a65882d0ef95d2b8e9b1ad5389feca1a9024fd4","tid":1930012,"uid":308404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:37:54.000Z","msg":"Same 老豆仲日日話咩係美國陰謀<br />\n專登傳入武漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好無奈"},{"pid":"b519448f482201e376f63c3b5cdfb8ab646e67e0","tid":1930012,"uid":268371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77e98c1b14c379a5030785abf71f1541625c4c89",